{"tid":1562894,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"見到同路人唔知點樣打氣？試下Fist Bump啦！","createTime":"2019-09-12T07:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T11:10:05.000Z","uid":173814,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ce3b2e05476e2b75ba02a37abe9a030bb3446f45","tid":1562894,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:58:04.000Z","msg":"有無試過見到連儂牆勤力貼貼既手足，好想打氣但係唔知點做好？<br />\n有無試過見到熟悉既前線手足，除左一個喂之外，唔知點打招呼？<br />\n有無試過幫襯黃底餐廳，想俾佢知有自己友支持，但係毒撚怕醜？<br />\n有無試過見到跳閘師兄，佢急急腳走，你又想支持一下，可以點呢？<br />\n<br />\n介紹一下美國人打招呼方法：Fist Bump<br />\n我地交俾Obama先生示範一下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YmnaAbFjwGs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYmnaAbFjwGs&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FWCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=b72d5440\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YmnaAbFjwGs</a><br />\n動作好簡單，主動伸出你既拳頭，等對方同樣伸出佢既拳頭，輕輕一碰，禮成。<br />\n美國人就好興fist bump時加一句&quot;How's it going?&quot; 之類既說話去打開話題。<br />\n我地手足們當然要用番我地既口號啦！<br />\n正如烏克蘭既先行例子：<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭朋友提議，將「光復香港 時代革命」變成義士之間打招呼用語<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1336769\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1336769</a><br />\n<br />\n我地可以結合成一個完整動作<br />\nＡ：主動伸出你既拳頭，＂光復香港＂<br />\nＢ：同樣伸出拳頭，＂時代革命＂，兩個拳頭輕輕一碰，禮成。<br />\n<br />\n既衛生，又有型，最近要係俾大家知道身邊有好多同路人！<br />\nＷＥ　ＡＲＥ　ＮＯＴ　ＡＬＯＮＥ！"},{"pid":"86a6304707f15c14b4fd599efa853f09014afe09","tid":1562894,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:58:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"0609e07b595cf305ddcda28eba5587ece8ec2b86","tid":1562894,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:59:43.000Z","msg":"好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7d03808fa64931c683010588088819470d08d2","tid":1562894,"uid":320135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0609e07b595cf305ddcda28eba5587ece8ec2b86","tid":1562894,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:59:43.000Z","msg":"好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:02:50.000Z","msg":"個個都咁做就唔嘔心"},{"pid":"e0b0fa0602e1310e57999b6e6bd4ade6e7b4eb9b","tid":1562894,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0609e07b595cf305ddcda28eba5587ece8ec2b86","tid":1562894,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:59:43.000Z","msg":"好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:05:40.000Z","msg":"全球好多地方都用緊呢個方式打招呼，唔好咁古板啦"},{"pid":"d4a19c134985de4c180f4c53bdb73f8da41261ad","tid":1562894,"uid":8175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:06:55.000Z","msg":"g chi!"},{"pid":"5aa9dc4b01d1eb5b99a81b3e167d99b98ccd3cae","tid":1562894,"uid":238613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5cfacaf21f95d0b4f1646619be6d26931fd8042","tid":1562894,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4a19c134985de4c180f4c53bdb73f8da41261ad","tid":1562894,"uid":8175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"